overview: Trouble's afoot when Kenzie Reeves finds herself in detention with mischievous Kali Roses and Emily Willis. The claws come out and clothes come off when Kristen Scott discovers that Jane Wilde never returned one of her favorite dresses; and, Gina Valentina has to strip down to the bare minimum so that spying roommate, Lily Rader can finally take a hint!
title: Already in Trouble
